<figureCitation id="92B0183CBB60411BEE979CCC2C9F25E9" captionStart="Figures 351–355" captionStartId="F61" captionText="Figures 351 - 355. Ophiomyia kalia Lonsdale, sp. nov., male genitalia 351 ejaculatory apodeme 352 hypandrium, ventral 353 hypandrial complex, left lateral 354 phallus and proepiphallus, ventral 355 external genitalia, ventral." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1051.64603.figures351-355" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/572160" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Figs 351-355</figureCitation>
