<paragraph id="29B957FD7BA7CC3BD9456C7B42352D71" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="822D6B25B0DDB868896C09B66EDAF8C8" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">The specific epithet is Greek for bird nest, referring to the nest from where the holotype was collected.</paragraph>
